Here is the translation:

The fifth day has come to the family's auspicious occasion, delighting the astrologer; 
It is being done as per the family tradition, and the children are playing with their toys on that war.

Here is the translation:

Lord has taken His seat right there below, child runs around all trees; 
That's how the day passed in which I was bewildered, He came that very moment being uninvited.

Here is the translation:

It has come in confusion that I am playing, it is in my mind to subdue Hari; 
The actions of others are his anger, it is to provoke and confront with opposition.

Here is the translation:

The storm came and joined with rain, making a lot of sparks; 
It stays in the wilderness, very stubbornly, there is no need for complaint.

Here is the translation:

Year after year clouds stay not pleased with the land, many things have gone on earth; 
Clouds become angry very loudly, wind speedily takes down trees and gets stuck.

Here is the translation:

It sits at its foot, a child staying there, without getting spoiled by even one tangle; 
Just like Govardhan stays beneath His feet, staying there in his place, always.

Those people are troubled then, the children cry; 
They make a bundle and tie it up tightly. 
They ask where they got this from, and bring it here; 
Now what shall I say, let me go to my village.

This is what it means:

This strong person will give happiness, sorrow will be scattered in the crowd of heart; 
Then I was who had knowledge of Hari, stuck that way became equal to even death.
